data.description: *** SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!*** Don't miss out on this 4 bed 3 bathroom sitting on a .65 acre lot in a quiet cul-de-sac on the outer edge of Grantsville. Priced to sell! Including plenty of parking space for all your outdoor toys with enough room to store all you need at home! Within four wheeling distance from the West Canyon Trail and just a minutes drive from the heart of Grantsville. Chicken coop and run included, hot tub included. Basement condition ready to be updated and perfect for anyone looking for an opportunity to build value while making it your own. NEW ROOF TO BE INSTALLED IN NOVEMBER. Downstairs bathroom lighting and plumbing fixtures to be installed before closing.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from ______________ .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
